/>"},{"pid":"b363d85f801738b01e4f557ec20fe3f92a20970e","tid":1630212,"uid":244357,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:56:56.000Z","msg":"幾年前睇過a very short introduction系列入面本Anarchism，但已經無咩印象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n剩返少少既記憶:<br />\n-係制度消失既情況下， 人類係有互相幫助既本能<br />\n(好似係有個西班牙既饑荒例子)<br />\n-有一本叫Mutual Aid 既書係重要參考文本，中譯應該係互助論<br />\n-強調解放工作人口(你都應該估到anarchism係左翼思想)<br />\n-有呢種主張既人其實唔覺得有機會推廣到大眾，但係會以自己方式係生活中去做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思，真係記得好少<br />\n除左無政府主義同英文名anarchism,你仲可以google 下個音譯，安那奇，或者會多少少資源"},{"pid":"e1b97ca7dea08e148b93968e5305f2a276374df2","tid":1630212,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:12:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果星期一晚18區開花失敗  就代表大家默許左呢條惡法</span><br />\n因為第日市面會如常運作<br />\n大家星期五講到有幾嬲有幾難接受 原來到上班日馬照跑舞照跳既?<br />\ncarrie仲有咩好驚呀?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">10月7號 18區啊 夜晚8點呀</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/33EUVX5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F33EUVX5.jpg&h=293eada8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">18區呀<br />\n18區呀</span></span><br />\n罷工文宣啊<br />\n行動Post呀<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">求下大家打返一場靚既三罷 起碼要8.5既級數先</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n強烈建議和武合一令星期二香城真正變死城<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejhbfS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejhbfS</a><br />\n<br />\n聽日一撚定要夜晚18區開花<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ajpvKkU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ajpvKkU</a><br />\n<br />\n聽日有咩活動有冇人知嫁？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631505\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631505</a><br />\n<br />\n18區開花 裝修手足入嚟接Job<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630461\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630461</a><br />\n<br />\n聽日一撚定要夜晚18區開花<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ajpvKkU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ajpvKkU</a>"},{"pid":"c33335bcfc9f29fe6b67a32695fa69ddeb89e509","tid":1630212,"uid":59832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:58:11.000Z","msg":"咩無政府主義先得架<br />\n<br />\n工團主義又好，無政府共產又好，無政府資本又好，mutualism都好<br />\n<br />\n唔同流派可以好唔同個喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3edc76b5d9ac5a1f74a05982715abcdefedbd6ef","tid":1630212,"uid":59832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dc2c74d0105dd75083020fc92ed4ac84a87c924d","tid":1630212,"uid":181156,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:11:18.000Z","msg":"原始人社會，完<br />\n不推文"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T20:05:27.000Z","msg":"其實anarchism唔係提倡原始人社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無政府主義嘅中心思想係反對任何不正當的階級。<br />\n<br />\n當中互助主義（mutualism）比較貼近原始人嘅社會制度，而Anarcho-primitivism先係提倡回歸原始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"352a965ccb00eccbc6149488d9dd538a6be83224","tid":1630212,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8690c7c9fce514c47324ae5ef3b962064d913a2","tid":1630212,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"523fc471d820c29ee4c46e698cadf9444c58de05","tid":1630212,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1069dfdc81093b280ddde10e705b770c3cbe92e","tid